necessity**\\n\\nIt seems like the user might have sent a message to confirm something. I need to figure out if they want an answer for the current session or if it’s something from a previous interaction. They probably want a real-time status update. If that’s the case, I can let them know “ejecutado en canal externo,” as this might indicate the delivery was successful. I want to make sure I get this right for them!\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \" ejecutado en canal externo.\",\n              \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0821345abba5ec180169c805fb83248191becbecb8b13ccea9\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n          \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n          \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 29765,\n            \"output\": 65,\n            \"totalTokens\": 29830,\n            \"cacheRead\": 0,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0.07538750000000001\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774716403526,\n          \"responseId\": \"resp_0821345abba5ec180169c805f57e1c8191b5a721bd5b7e93f6\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"b3909cea\",\n            \"seq\": 139\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:tui-104fc32a-4543-4770-a2ca-02f8fde7383b\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774716570036,\n      \"sessionId\": \"792032df-f362-4870-ab66-658780af0351\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 272000,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0.003168,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1774363124606,\n      \"endedAt\": 1774363129589,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 4983,\n      \"childSessions\": [\n        \"agent:main:subagent:9dc03af6-f7ea-43a5-b470-4a2a2b60927e\"\n      ],\n      \"systemSent\": false,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\main\\\\sessions\\\\792032df-f362-4870-ab66-658780af0351.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"❌ Failed to submit approval: GatewayClientRequestError: unknown or expired approval id\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1774716570415,\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 0,\n            \"output\": 0,\n            \"totalTokens\": 0,\n            \"cacheRead\": 0,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"api\": \"openai-responses\",\n          \"provider\": \"openclaw\",\n          \"model\": \"gateway-injected\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"6f3c9fcd\",\n            \"seq\": 1\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:b824f7b0-7497-4984-b0ff-d1bd45539f3c\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: daily-email-review-and-whatsapp-reminder\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: daily-email-review-and-whatsapp-reminder\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774702867117,\n      \"sessionId\": \"5aaab360-e355-4f77-8595-be24d86e481f\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 272000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 15227,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0.35624350000000005,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\main\\\\sessions\\\\5aaab360-e355-4f77-8595-be24d86e481f.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Necesito aprobación para revisar Gmail/Calendar con `gog`.\\n\\nEjecuta exactamente esto:\\n\\n`/approve allow-once powershell -NoProfile -Command \\\"$env:GOG_ACCOUNT='atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com';\\nWrite-Host '=== FORWARDED / IMPORTANT INBOX ===';\\ngog gmail messages search 'in:inbox (from:toledo970501@gmail.com OR subject:Fwd OR subject:RV: OR subject:FW: OR subject:Fwd:) newer_than:14d' --max 50 --account atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com;\\nWrite-Host '=== TODAY / DEADLINE KEYWORDS ===';\\ngog gmail messages search 'in:inbox (today OR hoy OR deadline OR vence OR vencimiento OR due OR due date OR challenge OR interview OR prueba OR test OR task OR pendiente OR reminder OR meeting OR reunión OR factura OR payment OR pago) newer_than:30d' --max 50 --account atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com;\\nWrite-Host '=== UNREAD INBOX ===';\\ngog gmail messages search 'in:inbox is:unread newer_than:14d' --max 50 --account atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com;\\nWrite-Host '=== CALENDARS ===';\\ngog calendar list --account atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com\\\"` \\n\\nEn cuanto lo apruebes, sigo.\",\n              \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_054daf8cc27b147a0169c7d134298881918855f696ad716598\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n          \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n          \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 123,\n            \"output\": 296,\n            \"totalTokens\": 15523,\n            \"cacheRead\": 15104,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0.0085235\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774702892987,\n          \"responseId\": \"resp_054daf8cc27b14